FILENAME::2781
---
title: "MPI Collective Communications"
url: "http://hpcuniversity.org/trainingMaterials/39/"
creator: "Brandon Barker"
description: "Prerequisites: MPI Basics, C, Fortran

The purpose of collective communication is to manipulate a shared piece or set of information. In this module, we introduce these routines in three categories: synchronization, data movement, and global computation."
rights: "All contents copyright  Cornell University. All rights reserved.

